caption.p: Genomic characterization of Aedes aegypti totivirus (AaTV). ( A) Genome organization of AaTV. ( B) Phylogenetic analysis of AaTV. Maximum likelihood tree of AaTV constructed with the conserved amino acid domain of the genome sequence with Genbank accession number LC496074. The conserved domains were extracted using MAFFT 7 online version [ 27] and the Gblocks program [ 28]. Bootstrap support values from 1000 bootstrap replicates are indicated on the branches.
